channel.description:
[center] [img]http://img815.imageshack.us/img815/6883/wonderscapepktournament.png[/img] [b]Hello every one, i trying to release my first source :) So im noob in moparscape server coding :) Please just don't call me leacher, for some new things i just give to my self only 10% credits.I changed home, added animals to home, to make home viable.Fixed some bugs, make woodcuting and cooking trainable.I added top 10 online hightscores.When i using this source i had 15~30 players online.So thanks for every one who download :) Sorry my English suck's :D[/b]
[img]http://img846.imageshack.us/img846/4204/tournament.png[/img]
[b]Server Download Link(Source and Client):[/b] [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?mk6cj84hsbywq4c]http://www.mediafire.com/?mk6cj84hsbywq4c[/url]
[b]Server Features:[/b]
602 items added 525 gfx added 525 emotes added 602 npcs Ancient curse prayers under construction (only turmoil so far) Fixed Dragon hide equipping requirment Godwars dungeon added needs some work still New home - Lunar isle Added farming to new home Added Woodcutting to the new home also. Added Inferno Adze Fixed the godsword specs Added a few activity logs Fixed all dupes i am aware of Changed Exp rate from 300 to 800 + the server bonus, fairly good exp rate Cut down on some of the cache memory Added an Npc to sell barrows gloves for 20 - currently only way to get them (removed from pest control) Added a new starter that gives 50 to any combat stat you wish Added a casket system, Caskets drop from bosses and Abby demons and Dark beasts, rare drop - they can give you shit, or a rare item ;) Updated jads looks, only 1 wave also Perfect switching, good for hybriding Ability to Rush Redid some drops and drop rates 100% RUNESCAPE AUTOCASTING creds to underoath <3 Added new gfx and emote to teleports Warriors guild is added - also needs work Chaotic maul Updated some out-dated sprites, mostly in mage book Fixed glowing in the mage book Top 10 online hightscore
